codex
I found the core visual headers and UTCs. The main issues to resolve are small: a misleading “static image” note on `AnimatedImageVisual::SetResourceUrl`, overly narrow image properties, `PIXEL_AREA` wording, and a couple of claims that should reference `View::AddVisual` behavior rather than internal containers.
